1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,640
’In tlen nikijtoua xpara nochimej nemejuamej.

2
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:12,840
Nejua nikixmatstikaj inyojlo nochimej on yejuan yonikintlapejpenij.

3
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:17,120
Pero ika onkaj nochiuas on tlen kijtoua on Yektlajkuilojli:

4
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:18,880
“On yejuan nouan tlakua,

5
00:00:18,880 --> 00:00:21,120
yonokuep notlauelikniu.”

6
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:23,760
In nemechijlia aman ijkuak xe nochiua,

7
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,560
para ijkuak nochiuas,

8
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:29,160
nemejuamej nenkineltokaskej niakin nejua.

9
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:33,800
Ika tlen melauak nemechijlia ika yejuan kiselia on yejuan niktitlani,

10
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:35,240
no nechselia nejua.

11
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:37,520
Niman on yejuan nejua nechselia,

12
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:40,520
no kiselia on yejuan onechajtitlan.

13
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,440
Ijkuak ijkon yokijtoj,

14
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:45,040
Jesús sanoyej onoyolajman,

15
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:47,260
niman imixpan okijtoj:

16
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:49,560
—Ika tlen melauak nemechijlia,

17
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:51,800
semej nemejuamej nechtemakas.

18
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:55,280
Kemaj on nomachtijkej* opeu nootaj.

19
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:58,760
Yejuamej xkimatiyaj akinon kiteneuaya Jesús.

20
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:01,720
Niman semej inomachtijkauan*,

21
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,920
yejuan Jesús sanoyej kitlajsojtlaya*,

22
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:07,680
nemiya inakastlan kampa tlakuajtikatkaj.

23
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:14,680
Niman Simón Pedro okixnots para ma kitlajtolti akinon on yejuan kiteneuaya kitemakas.

24
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,480
Yejua ika,

25
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:20,240
on nomachtijketl más okinisiuij niman onotekak iyelpan Jesús,

26
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:22,120
niman okitlajtoltij:

27
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,720
—NoTEKO,

28
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:26,680
¿akinon on yejuan mitstemakas?

29
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,160
Jesús okinankilij:

30
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:31,080
—Nikpatsos se tlajkotipantsin pan,

31
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:33,120
niman on akin nikmakas,

32
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,400
on yejua.

33
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,440
Ijkon tej,

34
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:40,640
okipatsoj se tlajkotipantsin pan niman okimakak Judas Iscariote,

35
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,360
ikoneu Simón.

36
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:45,280
Niman ijkuak Judas yokikuaj on pan,

37
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:48,160
Satanás nimantsin okalak ipan iyojlo.

38
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:50,160
Kemaj Jesús okijlij:

39
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,920
—On tlen tikchiuas,

40
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,420
nimantsin xchiua.

41
00:01:53,420 --> 00:02:00,880
Pero nion semej on yejuan tlakuajtikatkaj ne ipan on mesa xokajsikamat tline* ijkon okijlij.

42
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:04,760
Judas kipiyaya on bolsa kampa kejeuaj tomin.

43
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,280
Yejua ika,

44
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:12,480
sekimej okinemilijkej ika Jesús kijliaya itlaj ma kouati yejuan kitekitiltiskej ipan on iluitl,

45
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:15,440
noso itlaj ma kinmaka on mayankej.

46
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:18,520
Ijkuak Judas yokikuaj on pan,

47
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,000
nimantsin okis.

48
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,680
Ijkuakon,

49
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,080
ye tlayoua katka.

50
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,960
Más sakin* ijkuak Judas yokis,

51
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,640
Jesús okijtoj:

52
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,920
—Aman noteititia noueyilis,

53
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:32,640
nejua yejuan oninochiu Tlakatl.

54
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:36,680
Niman iueyilis Dios no noteititia notechkopa.

55
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:40,000
Niman tla nejua nikteititia iueyilis Dios,

56
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,000
tla ijkon,

57
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,200
Dios no kiteititis noueyilis,

58
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:46,240
niman saniman ijki kichiuas.

59
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,880
Notlajsojkakoneuan,

60
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:50,520
xok ninemis miyek tonaltin nemouan.

61
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:53,360
Nemejuamej nennechtejtemoskej,

62
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:58,400
pero sano ijki ken onikimijlij on hebreos* no ijki nemechijlia aman:

63
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:00,960
Xuelis nenyaskej kampa nejua niau.

64
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,760
Nemechmaka in yenkuik tlanauatijli:

65
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:06,280
xmotlajsojtlakan* inuan oksekimej.

66
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,760
Ijkon ken nejua nemechtlajsojtla*,

67
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:12,400
nemejuamej no ijki xmotlajsojtlakan* inuan oksekimej.

68
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:15,200
Tla nemotlajsojtlaj inuan oksekimej,

69
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:19,080
nochi tlakatl kitas ika nennotemachtijkauan.

70
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:21,840
Simón Pedro okitlajtoltij Jesús:

71
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,960
—NoTEKO,

72
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,120
¿kanon tiau?

73
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:26,520
Niman Jesús okijlij:

74
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,400
—Kampa nejua niau,

75
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,760
xuelis tias aman,

76
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:32,280
pero más sakin* kemaj tias.

77
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,480
Kemaj Pedro okijlij:

78
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,520
—NoTEKO,

79
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,880
¿tline* xuelis nias aman?

80
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:42,140
Nikpiya noyojlo para nimikis san mopampa tla noneki.

81
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:44,160
Jesús okijlij:

82
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:47,920
—¿Melauak tikpiya moyojlo para timikis san nopampa?

83
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:51,560
Ika tlen melauak nimitsijlia ika antes tsajtsis on kaxtil*,

84
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:55,760
tejua yexpa tinechnenekis.

